              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Time the prompt",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " \u2014 show the rating prompt 30 seconds after the agent completes, not immediately; the user needs time to evaluate the output."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Thank, don't interrogate",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " \u2014 'Thanks for the rating! Anything specific?' converts more thumbs-down into useful comments than 'Please explain your rating'."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Sample, don't ask every time",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " \u2014 for high-volume agents, randomly sample 20% of sessions for feedback prompts. This gives statistical signal without fatiguing daily users."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Summary"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Explicit feedback gives you the ground truth signal needed to evaluate and improve agents over time. Use binary thumbs plus optional comment as the default \u2014 it minimises collection friction while capturing the cases that matter most. Persist records in an append-only store with prompt hashes so you can correlate ratings with specific input patterns. Monitor thumbs-up ratio continuously and alert on regressions. Reduce survey fatigue through optional prompts, session-level (not turn-level) collection, and statistical sampling for high-volume deployments."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}